      "rationale": "Solver verified against ASME V&V 20 benchmark cases for incompressible Navier-Stokes. Taylor-Green vortex and lid-driven cavity results confirm correct numerical implementation."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
