      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) reported for primary QoI with GCI < 5% on fine grid.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (4.2M, 9.8M, 21.4M cells). GCI for hemolysis index on fine mesh is 2.3%, exceeding MRL 2 requirement. Richardson extrapolation applied."
    },
    {
