      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions documented and boundary conditions traceable to physical measurements.",
      "rationale": "FDA GCBP experimental conditions (flow rate 2.5–7 L/min, pressure rise 0–270 mmHg, 3500 RPM) are fully documented. CFD boundary conditions set from measured inlet velocity profiles and outlet pressures."
